{"tid":1148704,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[仆街了］香港首例　上水屠房驗出有豬內臟帶病毒　將殺6000豬","createTime":"2019-05-10T15:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T15:47:19.000Z","uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afe133f974bf9fdfed38acb6cc74cc427859e7f3","tid":1148704,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"中國內地非洲豬瘟疫情蔓延全國，香港也失守，出現首宗非洲豬瘟，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始將於今晚10時，就一宗非洲豬瘟化驗報告會見傳媒。<br />\n據了解，上水屠房有廣東入口豬隻內臟，驗出帶有非洲豬瘟病毒，約6,000隻活豬將被人道毀滅。按之前所定，屠房將停止運作數日，以便進行消毒，即供應市場的活豬將銳減八成；荃灣屠房只可供應約400隻本地活豬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/327748/非洲豬瘟-香港首例-上水屠房驗出有豬內臟帶病毒-將殺6000豬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F327748%2F%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%A0%E6%88%BF%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E6%9C%89%E8%B1%AC%E5%85%A7%E8%87%9F%E5%B8%B6%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E5%B0%87%E6%AE%BA6000%E8%B1%AC&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=3a337e0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/327748/非洲豬瘟-香港首例-上水屠房驗出有豬內臟帶病毒-將殺6000豬</a><br />\n<br />\n好擔心.........📧"},{"pid":"877573442b09777b98ce98da5aae95fe68550285","tid":1148704,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"邊個開名我立即屌佢老母"},{"pid":"dfe35ff3efeae9db5df1d4dbc83eb706af557029","tid":1148704,"uid":99946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSqb6ap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSqb6ap.png&h=5a52cf4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d09143e9bbe4486344b764f98469a254f99814c","tid":1148704,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"加埋支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"